title: SSU.Design.Video.Thumbnails.Maker.v5.0.0.1.Incl.Crack-SND
description:
Video Thumbnails Maker allows you to make thumbnails (caps, previews, screen-lists) and screenshots of video files. The utility can be used for home-video cataloging and for network video sharing support.

INSTRUCTIONS:

1. Install VideoThumbnailsMaker_Setup.exe, when finished installing DO NOT RUN PROGRAM.

2. Copy the files in the CRACK folder to the installed directory. Usually: C:Program FilesVideo Thumbnails Maker. Do not copy the folder itself.

3. When prompted to overwrite files, say YES/ACCEPT.

4. Run program and you will see "Platinum" status and Platinum features are available i.e. no watermark in thumbnail sheet and platinum engine is unlocked.
